                        <interp inst="t18420822-name-1884" type="given" value="EDWARD"></interp>EDWARD ELLIOTT</persName>
                  </hi>. I am a policeman. I produce a certificate of the prisoner's former conviction, which I got from the office of the Clerk of the Peace for Surrey—(<hi rend="italic">read</hi>)—I was present at the trial—the prisoner is the person.</p>
